248
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,560
That pain.

249
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:31,680
So from a young age,

250
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:34,760
I was required to do my best,

251
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:35,880
and be most excellent.

252
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:39,000
I would compare with every friend

253
