life has meanings to me.

255
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:47,000
I won the first place in piano

256
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,760
and equestrian contests.

257
00:13:48,760 --> 00:13:50,440
Even for getting into this university,

258
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,960
I was the top one.

259
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:53,680
