268
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:21,320
Every time I saw him,

269
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,400
I would get beaten.

270
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:31,400
So in my memory,

271
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:35,200
only when he gave me money

272
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,560
did I feel that he was my father.

273
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:40,960
