275
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,840
But I'm not happy at all.

276
00:14:46,680 --> 00:14:47,640
Do you know why?

277
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,640
Because I know he did it

278
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:51,120
