279
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:54,680
It's just to make him feel good

280
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:57,080
in front of others.

281
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:00,440
My dad was an alcoholic when I was kid.

282
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:03,440
Every time he drank too much,

283
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,840
