409
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:16,400
I...

410
00:21:16,640 --> 00:21:18,000
Class head, you heard us?

411
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:18,880
Cla...class head.

412
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:20,400
