436
00:22:04,280 --> 00:22:05,760
Right, we are all confident.

437
00:22:06,080 --> 00:22:06,760
Miss.

438
00:22:07,080 --> 00:22:08,800
Even the last two are confident.

439
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:10,200
We're even more confident, right?

440
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:11,680
Exactly.

441
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,320
Alright.

442
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:14,320
I don't want to see anyone

443
00:22:14,320 --> 00:22:15,640
