448
00:22:38,560 --> 00:22:39,760
Do all that's needed.

449
00:22:42,528 --> 00:22:43,080
I...

450
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:44,000
What?

451
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:45,000
Always like this.

452
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:47,000
Don't come here again.

453
00:22:52,400 --> 00:22:53,000
Hello.

454
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:55,920
Hello, I...

