00:22:56,080 --> 00:22:57,440
Hey there, I'm Li Yanhao.

456
00:22:57,440 --> 00:22:58,160
He is Xiao Rang.

457
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:58,760
Right.

458
00:22:58,760 --> 00:23:00,560
We are the top students in our class.

459
00:23:00,560 --> 00:23:01,880
Mrs. Jiang likes us the most.

460
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:04,440
I just saw you chatting with her.

461
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,440
You are special someone of her, right?

462
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:07,640
Special, right?

463
00:23:08,280 --> 00:23:09,560
