474
00:23:33,800 --> 00:23:34,520
How is it?

475
00:23:36,080 --> 00:23:36,760
No way.

476
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:38,640
Before your final exams,

477
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:39,920
